vIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 dhwKVO image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">“It was fairly anarchic…” Nick Broomfield recalls Greek cinema under the stars with all-natural extras</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Nick Broomfield</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-and-sound/my-dream-palace/nick-broomfield-gardenia-open-air-cinema-hydra-greece-screenings" title="Read “It was fairly anarchic…” Nick Broomfield recalls Greek cinema under the stars with all-natural extras" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>“It was fairly anarchic…” Nick Broomfield recalls Greek cinema under the stars with all-natural extras</span></a></article><article image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-03/julie-cleaning-cineworld-seats.jpg/96x54-cropped/julie-cleaning-cineworld-seats.jpg" imageAltText="" standfirst="To mark the anniversary of the first coronavirus closures, we invited a range of voices from across UK film exhibition to share their experiences and hopes for the future." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard false"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 jDTRGK image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">Ten key cinema workers on the way out of lockdown</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Katie McCabe and Isabel Stevens</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-and-sound/interviews/ten-key-cinema-workers-future-after-lockdown" title="Read Ten key cinema workers on the way out of lockdown" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>Ten key cinema workers on the way out of lockdown</span></a></article><article image48x27="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-06/the-long-day-closes-1992-boy-in-theatre-balcony-light.jpg/96x54-cropped/the-long-day-closes-1992-boy-in-theatre-balcony-light.jpg" imageAltText="" standfirst="The dark is in sight! In the UK, cinemas have a provisional reopening date of 17 May. To celebrate, we count down 80 memorable movie-theatre scenes in the movies." class="ArticleCard__Outer-sc-zrtbni-0 eIZIIS articleCard false"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImageContainer-sc-zrtbni-5 ehvIXQ"><div class="ArticleCard__PageImage-sc-zrtbni-6 dndRAA image"></div></div><h3 class="ArticleCard__Heading-sc-zrtbni-3 bynrVe">Let there be projector light: 80 films that take us inside cinemas</h3><div class="ArticleCard__Meta-sc-zrtbni-1 edgoES"><p class="ArticleCard__Author-sc-zrtbni-2 KIAzD">By Thomas Flew</p></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-and-sound/lists/cinema-scenes-in-movies" title="Read Let there be projector light: 80 films that take us inside cinemas" class="ArticleCard__CallToAction-sc-zrtbni-4 fwpHHm"><span>Let there be projector light: 80 films that take us inside cinemas</span></a></article></div><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/articles/category/my-dream-palace" class="Button__PrimaryButton-sc-8dp7u4-0 iGKFPz ArticleGrid__CentredButton-sc-nctj0m-2 CtQWL">See more</a></div><div class="getPromoBanner__BannerWrapper-sc-12jtskq-5 fTaJVz promoBannerWrapper "><div style="background-image:url(https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2020-09/weekly-film-bulletin-banner.jpg/1504x846-cropped/weekly-film-bulletin-banner.jpg)" class="getPromoBanner__BackgroundImage-sc-12jtskq-6 hOnoGv"></div><div data-theme="0" class="getPromoBanner__PromoWrapper-sc-12jtskq-0 cCXqgu"><h2 class="getPromoBanner__H2-sc-12jtskq-1 ihlpMV">The Weekly Film Bulletin</h2><p class="getPromoBanner__Description-sc-12jtskq-3 bnpyYf">Sign up below for a free extra helping of Sight and Sound, keeping you in touch with the latest film news, reviews and features from our archive.</p